### Upload medical attachment to care request
POST /api/medical-attachments/upload
Authorization: Bearer <owner-token>
Content-Type: multipart/form-data

file=@lab-report.pdf;type=application/pdf
care_request_id=<care-request-id>

### Attach existing attachment to health record
POST /api/medical-attachments/<attachment-id>/attach
Authorization: Bearer <owner-or-assigned-vet-or-admin-token>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "health_record_id": "<health-record-id>"
}

### List medical attachments in appointment scope
GET /api/medical-attachments?appointment_id=<appointment-id>
Authorization: Bearer <owner-or-assigned-vet-or-admin-token>

### Download attachment
GET /api/medical-attachments/<attachment-id>/download
Authorization: Bearer <owner-or-assigned-vet-or-admin-token>

### Delete attachment
DELETE /api/medical-attachments/<attachment-id>
Authorization: Bearer <owner-or-assigned-vet-or-admin-token>

### Simulate appointment reminder
POST /api/appointments/<appointment-id>/reminders/simulate
Authorization: Bearer <owner-or-assigned-vet-or-admin-token>
